Class AbstractRefinementPolicy

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.wala.demandpa.alg.refinepolicy.AbstractRefinementPolicy
All Implemented Interfaces:
RefinementPolicy
Direct Known Subclasses:
ManualRefinementPolicy, SinglePassRefinementPolicy, TunedRefinementPolicy
public abstract class AbstractRefinementPolicy extends Object implements RefinementPolicy
Default RefinementPolicy implementation, delegating to some provided FieldRefinePolicy and CallGraphRefinePolicy
Author:
manu
